{"tid":1865845,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[后果自負] 警破出售捕獵野味案　檢逾千隻野生動物","createTime":"2020-02-06T11:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T11:56:30.000Z","uid":275872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8350b0b5c7ef7b91ae21240cbd6116b84f7a2ed1","tid":1865845,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢肺炎疫情持續蔓延，當局嚴查各地非法捕獵或交易野味。江蘇宿遷市一間飯店近日就被揭有野兔、黑翅鳶、黃鼬等野味出售，警方立即上門搗破，再循線破獲兩宗非法捕獵和經營野味案，查獲野味加工和10多處存儲窩點，檢獲逾1000隻野味，超過20人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方接獲民眾爆料稱，當地一間飯店仍有野味出售，立即派員上門調查，當場冰櫃中發現4隻已處理的野兔。飯店老闆事後被帶回警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方隨後查獲兩宗相關案件，檢獲野兔、黑翅鳶、黃鼬、水雞、野鴨等野味，其中有兩隻為國家二級保護動物，逾20名涉案者被捕，其中9人被採取刑事強制措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206192013868-0206_00952_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200206%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200206192013868-0206_00952_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news%26eventID%3D402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAslRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=871b212b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206192013868-0206_00952_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883476ed4097c016f5a39f2c63fde</a>"},{"pid":"d3d34c30d7d583dd984f9e4e6094984917ab7232","tid":1865845,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"文明飲食"},{"pid":"2dd09ec95882df2ae5d68655d1b65496a8a92373","tid":1865845,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccafc38229cee0b0812bd83e18a6d91152721e6f","tid":1865845,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:56:30.000Z",